headline: Compare and Save: Switching Rate Plan May Lower PG&E Customers' Bills
summary: One simple change could make a big difference in your energy bill. Pacific Gas and Electric Company (PG&E) is encouraging customers to check that they are on the lowest-cost rate plan for their home or business.
